<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/782889-i-m-rereading-the-gastronomical-me-for-the">I&#39;m rereading The Gastronomical Me for the umpteenth time. It has only now occurred to me to wonder how it is that a small, Quaker farm town like Whittier, Calif., produced both her and Richard Nixon, within five years of age of each other. Do you think the two families were acquainted?</a>
</div>
