<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">She wasn&apos;t really. Born in Albion, Michigan, a small town. Migrated to California with her family. Her father was a newspaper publisher. Pretty sure N<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">She wasn't really. Born in Albion, Michigan, a small town. Migrated to California with her family. Her father was a newspaper publisher. Pretty sure Nixons were unknown to them.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
