        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer680238868" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5468668666946675">This book is lovely.<br/><br/>M.F.K. Fisher writes about food and eating in such a wonderful, approachable, delighted way -- it&apos;s great to read food writing written by someone whose first tenant so clearly is: I LOVE FOOD.</span>
  <span id="freeText5468668666946675" style="display:none">This book is lovely.<br /><br />M.F.K. Fisher writes about food and eating in such a wonderful, approachable, delighted way -- it's great to read food writing written by someone whose first tenant so clearly is: I LOVE FOOD.</span>
