              <span id="reviewTextContainer228831137" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5922316719024271872">A compendium of Fisher&apos;s writings, this book - with its eloquent language and many a digression - is less about the recipes than the accompanying musings. Her tales of living in France make me want to spend more time there and her A to Z: An alphabet for gourmets are little gems of writing.</span>
  <span id="freeText5922316719024271872" style="display:none">A compendium of Fisher's writings, this book - with its eloquent language and many a digression - is less about the recipes than the accompanying musings. Her tales of living in France make me want to spend more time there and her A to Z: An alphabet for gourmets are little gems of writing.</span>
